  "original_title": "\u0db1\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dbd\u0dca \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0db4\u0dcf\u0dbd \u0dc3\u0db8\u0dca\u0db6\u0db1\u0dca\u0db0\u0dba\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0d85\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dc3\u0dca \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dc1\u0db1\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A bribery investigation regarding Nimal Siripala",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Bribery or Corruption Allegations Investigation Commission started an investigation today (15) regarding the bribery charge leveled against Minister Nimal Siripala de Silva.",
        "The Commission has started this investigation based on a complaint made by the Anti-Corruption Front.",
        "Accordingly, a spokesperson of the commission told Lankadeepa that a statement is to be recorded from Minister Nimal Siripala de Silva in the future.",
        "The allegation was related to an incident where a bribe was demanded from the Japanese company Taisei, which is carrying out the construction work of Katunayake Airport.",
        "In this regard, the Bribery or Corruption Allegations Investigation Commission hopes to inquire from the representatives of that company as well as from the officials of the Japanese Embassy in Sri Lanka in the future.",
        "When the allegation was made, Minister Nimal Siripala de Silva resigned from the ministry as a measure to allow an independent investigation to be conducted.",
        "After that, President Ranil Wickramasinghe appointed a three-member committee headed by retired High Court Judge Mrs. Kusala Sarojani Weerawardena to investigate the allegation and Mr. Nimal Siripala Silva was acquitted of the bribery charge and the report of that committee was released recently.",
        "Accordingly, Mr. Nimal Siripala de Silva was recently re-appointed to the post of Minister of Ports, Shipping and Aviation by President Ranil Wickramasinghe."
      ],
